    {
      "status_url": "https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/116801594265056664",
      "url": "https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/116801594265056664",
      "avatar": "https://hketf-lab.pages.dev/assets/home/trump-home.jpg",
      "created_at": "2026-06-23T21:41:29.148Z",
      "created_at_text": "Jun 23, 2026, 9:41 PM",
      "content": "Isn't it strange, the Dumocrats are running a man in Texas who looks virtually identical to Alfred E. Neuman, of MAD Magazine fame and, in Georgia, they're running someone who looks like a twin to the Late, Great, Pee-wee Herman. With these two horrible Political Candidates, I don't know if there's a genetic tree, but it certainly is close! What do you think? In any event, Mike Collins, of Georgia, should easily beat Pee-wee, and Ken Paxton, of Texas, should easily beat Alfred E. Vote Republican and, MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN! President DONALD J. TRUMP",
      "content_html": "Isn't it strange, the Dumocrats are running a man in Texas who looks virtually identical to Alfred E. Neuman, of MAD Magazine fame and, in Georgia, they're running someone who looks like a twin to the Late, Great, Pee-wee Herman. With these two horrible Political Candidates, I don't know if there's a genetic tree, but it certainly is close! What do you think? In any event, Mike Collins, of Georgia, should easily beat Pee-wee, and Ken Paxton, of Texas, should easily beat Alfred E. Vote Republican and, MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN! President DONALD J. TRUMP",
      "media": [
        {
          "url": "https://hketf-lab.pages.dev/api/pulse/trump-media?id=aHR0cHM6Ly90cnV0aC1hcmNoaXZlLnVzLWlhZC0xLmxpbm9kZW9iamVjdHMuY29tL2F0dGFjaG1lbnRzLzE2Nzg4LzU3ZTg0MTVjM2FlZDM5ZWIuanBn",
          "type": "image"
        },
        {
          "url": "https://hketf-lab.pages.dev/api/pulse/trump-media?id=aHR0cHM6Ly90cnV0aC1hcmNoaXZlLnVzLWlhZC0xLmxpbm9kZW9iamVjdHMuY29tL2F0dGFjaG1lbnRzLzE2Nzg5LzY1NDAzOGJjNDQyOGY4ZWYuanBn",
          "type": "image"
        }
      ],
      "favourites_count": 11017,
      "reblogs_count": 3072,
      "replies_count": 1898,
      "content_zh_cn": "这不是很奇怪吗？那些“蠢主党”（Dumocrats）在得州推出来的一个人，看上去几乎和《MAD》杂志里大名鼎鼎的阿尔弗雷德·E·纽曼一模一样；而在佐治亚州，他们推出的另一个人，看上去则像已故伟大的“皮威·赫尔曼”的孪生兄弟。\n\n面对这两位糟糕透顶的政治候选人，我不知道他们之间是不是有什么“基因谱系”，但看起来确实八九不离十！你怎么看？\n\n无论如何，佐治亚州的迈克·柯林斯应该能轻松击败“皮威”，得州的肯·帕克斯顿也应该能轻松击败“阿尔弗雷德·E”。投票给共和党人，让美国再次伟大！\n\n总统 唐纳德·J·特朗普",
      "content_zh_hk": "這不是很奇怪嗎？那些「蠢主黨」（Dumocrats）在得州推出的一個人，看上去幾乎和《MAD》雜誌中廣為人知的阿爾弗雷德·E·紐曼一模一樣；而在佐治亞州，他們推出的另一個人，看上去則像已故偉大的「皮威·赫爾曼」的孿生兄弟。\n\n面對這兩位糟糕透頂的政治候選人，我不知道他們之間是否有什麼「基因樹」，但看起來確實非常接近！你怎麼看？\n\n無論如何，佐治亞州的邁克·柯林斯應該能輕鬆擊敗「皮威」，得州的肯·帕克斯頓也應該能輕鬆擊敗「阿爾弗雷德·E」。投票給共和黨，讓美國再次偉大！\n\n總統 唐納德·J·特朗普",
      "content_ko": "이상하지 않나요? 그 ‘덤ocrats’는 텍사스에서 MAD 매거진으로 유명한 알프레드 E. 뉴먼과 거의 똑같이 생긴 사람을 내세우고, 조지아에서는 고(故) 위대한 피위 허먼의 쌍둥이처럼 보이는 사람을 내세우고 있습니다.\n\n이 두 끔찍한 정치 후보를 보면, 무슨 유전적 계보가 있는지는 모르겠지만, 확실히 아주 가까워 보입니다! 어떻게 생각하시나요?\n\n어쨌든 조지아의 마이크 콜린스는 ‘피위’를 쉽게 이길 것이고, 텍사스의 켄 팩스턴은 ‘알프레드 E.’를 쉽게 이길 것입니다. 공화당에 투표하고, 미국을 다시 위대하게 만드십시오!\n\n도널드 J. 트럼프 대통령",
      "source_hint": "cnn"
    },
